OL,6,FA Northern Ireland Assembly minister
OL,7,Fhas been censured by the Assistant
OL,8,FLocal Government Commissioner for
OL,9,FStandards after admitting to breaching
OL,10,Fthe Northern Ireland Local Government
OL,11,FCode of Conduct for Councillors.
OL,13,FAlliance MLA Patrick Brown's breach
OL,14,Fcame in 2019 when he was a member of
OL,15,FNewry, Mourne and Down District
OL,16,FCouncil.
