OL,6,FHe posted on social media how he
OL,7,Fthough Sinn Fein, UUP, SDLP and DUP
OL,8,Fcouncillors had voted during the
OL,9,Fappointment of the Council's new Chief
OL,10,FExecutive Mrs Marie Ward.
