OL,3,CMLA censured for breaching code of
OL,4,Cconduct
OL,6,F"I apologise to the selection panel
OL,7,Ffor undermining their role and
OL,8,Fsuggesting that the panel made a
OL,9,Fchoice of Chief Executive based on
OL,10,Fpolitical lines. I accept that the
OL,11,Fselection process was merit based and
OL,12,Fthat my comments were open to
OL,13,Falternative interpretation. I,
OL,14,Ftherefore wish to set the record
OL,15,Fstraight and I apologise specifically
OL,16,Fto the members of the Selection Panel."
OL,18,FMr Brown is an MLA for South Down.
